name: adidas One Bball Sweatpants
description:
Perfectly Sporty

The adidas Basketball Joggers is perfect for chilly winter days. Its cozy fabric is meant to keep you warm and comfortable even when the temperature drops. The stylish design adds a tailored touch to your regular streetwear and lets you show off your look every time you step out the doors.
Intentionally designed to be very oversized. For a fit that is comfortably loose but less extreme, order 2 sizes down for women or 1 size down for men.

adidas Basketball Joggers Features:

  • 65% recycled polyester, 35% cotton fleece
  • Relaxed fit
  • Low rise
  • Ribbed waist with a drawcord
  • Front and back pockets

name: Jordan Sport Crossover
description: From training to simply hanging with your crew, you need a hoodie that does it all. Smooth on the outside with tiny unbrushed loops on the inside, this French terry layer comes packed with our sweat-wicking tech to help you stay fresh whatever you're doing. Benefits: Nike Dri-FIT technology moves sweat away from your skin for quicker evaporation, helping you stay dry and comfortable. Loopback fleece is breathable and provides lightweight warmth. Product details: Body: 62% cotton/38% polyester. Pocket bag, knuckle side: 100% cotton. Hood lining: 100% cotton. Front pocket. Ribbed cuffs and hem. Machine wash. Imported

name: Nike Club Fleece
description: Made with a slightly roomy fit, these lightweight fleece joggers from our Nike Club Collection give you the familiar feel you love, with a little extra space to lounge. To look and feel your best, pull them on with the matching Club Fleece Hoodie and your favourite Nike sneakers. Benefits: Smooth on the outside, brushed soft on the inside, this lightweight fleece is an easy layer when you want a little extra warmth. Designed to feel relaxed through the seat and thighs with a slight taper to the ribbed ankle cuffs. The soft elastic waistband with an outer drawcord helps you tighten up to the right feel. Product details: Body: 80% cotton/20% polyester. Side Pocket Knuckle Side: 100% cotton. Back Pocket: 100% cotton. Machine wash. Imported

name: adidas Essentials
description:
Sustainable Street Style

The adidas ESS PT Pants bring classic comfort to your everyday rotation. Made from a blend of Better Cotton and recycled polyester, these slim-fit pants offer both style and sustainability in one chic package. The elastic waist with a drawcord ensures a customizable fit, while ribbed cuffs complete the sleek design. Flaunting an embroidered Trefoil logo on the left leg, these pants honor adidas' heritage with a modern twist. Experience comfort with an eco-conscious touch with the adidas ESS PT Pants.

adidas ESS PT Pants Features:

  • 70% cotton/30% recycled polyester
  • Slim fit
  • Elastic waist with drawcord
  • Ribbed cuffs
  • Side pockets
  • Embroidered stacked Trefoil on left leg
  • Machine wash

Sourced through Better Cotton via mass balance

name: Nike Tech Fleece
description:
Fleece Flair

Get eco-friendly warmth and comfort on the go with the Nike Sportswear Tech Fleece Joggers. Featuring a mix of recycled polyester and organic cotton fibers for a touch of sustainability, these premium fleece joggers feel smooth and warm without the bulk. The signature streamlined fit delivers a sleek, tailored look. The iconic paneled design and articulated knees offer that unmistakable Tech Fleece vibe you love, while tapering from the knee to ankle provides a fitted look, so you flaunt your sneakers with confidence.

Nike Sportswear Tech Fleece Joggers Features:

  • Body: 53% cotton/47% polyester; pocket bag knuckle side: 100% cotton
  • This product is made with at least 50% sustainable materials, using a blend of both recycled polyester and organic cotton fibers. The blend is at least 10% recycled fibers or at least 10% organic cotton fibers.
  • Imported
  • Streamlined Fit
  • Elastic waistband with an outer drawcord
  • Taped pocket with an interior organizer
  • Nike Futura logo at the left thigh
  • Tapering from the knee to ankle
  • Ribbed cuffs
  • Machine wash

name: Nike Tech Woven
description: Crafted from stretchy, breathable material, the Nike Tech Woven Jacket offers you ease of movement and adjustable details. Bungee cords with cord locks create a custom fit at the hem and hood. Benefits: Lightweight fabric moves sweat away from your skin for quick evaporation, helping you stay dry and comfortable. Loose fit through the body allows a full range of movement. Articulated elbows are made with movement in mind, and add a distinct Nike Tech aesthetic. Hood and stand collar offer coverage from the elements. Two-way zip lets you adjust your fit. Bungee cords with cord locks create a custom fit at the hem and hood. Product details: Nike Futura logo. Body: 94% nylon/6% elastane. Pockets: 100% polyester. Machine wash. Imported Windrunner origins: The Windrunner became the face of Nike apparel in 1978, at a time when the company was known for its footwear. Today, this running-turned-everyday jacket is still as relevant and exciting as it was back then, with its iconic 26-degree chevron styling, excellent breathability and weather resistance.

name: Nike Club
description: Easy to style and comfortable to wear, our Nike Club knit joggers are ready to become a versatile piece of your casual wardrobe. name: Nike Air Max Tuned 1
description:
Celebrating a Legend

Let your bold and edgy energy make waves with the Nike Air Max Plus. Inspired by beach life, these cool sneakers celebrate the glorious four decades of the Pegasus— Nike’s iconic running shoes. Sporting wavy design lines, the synthetic leather and mesh upper is packed with supreme comfort and a cool look. Offering signature cushioning, the Max Air unit ensures proper responsiveness with every stride. Fitted with a grippy rubber outsole, the Nike Air Max Plus has everything you need to flaunt your moves with confidence.

Nike Air Max Plus Features:

  • Synthetic leather and knit mesh upper
  • Wavy lines across the upper
  • Max Air unit
  • Plastic arch on the midsole
  • Rubber outsole

name: Nike Air Max Tuned 1
description: Let your attitude have the edge with flame-like caging that adds heat to the streets while airy mesh keeps you cool. The Nike Air Max Plus gives you a tuned Nike Air experience that offers premium stability and unbelievable cushioning. Benefits: Bringing stress-free beach life to the city, the supportive midfoot arch draws inspiration from a whale's tail. Design lines of the iconic plastic cage nod to palm trees and ocean waves. Originally designed for performance running, Nike Air units provide lightweight cushioning that lasts. Synthetic upper with lightweight mesh adds breathability and durability. Rubber outsole gives you durable traction. Nike Air Max Origins: Revolutionary Air technology first made its way into Nike footwear in 1978. The Air Max 1 debuted with visible Air technology in its heel, allowing fans more than just the feel of Air cushioning—suddenly they could see it. Since then, next-generation Air Max shoes have become a hit with athletes and collectors by offering striking colour combinations and reliable, lightweight cushioning.

The Nike Air Max Plus Utility blends your love for city explorations and beach fun. Made for your urban adventures, these beach-life-inspired sneakers ooze cool ruggedness. Featuring wavy lines, a nod to palm trees and ocean waves, the upper is dressed in real and synthetic leather with airy knits and mesh for complete comfort and support. The visible Max Air units in the forefoot and heel offer a Tuned Air experience, so you experience the ultimate cushioning sensation in every step.

Nike Air Max Plus Utility Features:

  • Real and synthetic leather with airy knits and mesh on the upper
  • Extra lace set tightened with a toggle and fed through loops anchored to the suede mudguard
  • Max Air units in the forefoot and heel
  • Plastic arch on the midsole
  • Foam in the midsole
  • Rubber outsole

name: Nike Air Max Tuned 1
description: Let your attitude have the edge with flame-like caging that adds heat to the streets while airy mesh keeps you cool. The Nike Air Max Plus gives you a tuned Nike Air experience that offers premium stability and unbelievable cushioning. Benefits: Bringing stress-free beach life to the city, the supportive midfoot arch draws inspiration from a whale's tail. Design lines of the iconic plastic cage nod to palm trees and ocean waves. Originally designed for performance running, Nike Air units provide lightweight cushioning that lasts. Synthetic upper with lightweight mesh adds breathability and durability. Rubber outsole gives you durable traction. Nike Air Max Origins: Revolutionary Air technology first made its way into Nike footwear in 1978. The Air Max 1 debuted with visible Air technology in its heel, allowing fans more than just the feel of Air cushioning—suddenly they could see it. Since then, next-generation Air Max shoes have become a hit with athletes and collectors by offering striking colour combinations and reliable, lightweight cushioning.

name: Nike Air Max 90
description: The Air Max 90 stays true to its running roots with the iconic Waffle sole. Stitched overlays and textured accents create the '90s look you love. Finished with easy-to-style colours, its visible Max Air cushioning adds comfort to your journey. Benefits: The textile upper with leather and synthetic overlays creates a layered look that lasts. Originally designed for performance running, visible Max Air cushioning puts the history of comfort beneath your feet. Rubber Waffle outsole delivers durable traction and heritage style. Product details: Padded collar. Foam midsole Air Max 90: The '90s were a turning point in culture—art, music, fashion and sneakers. The Air Max was at the forefront of the movement. With even more exposed Air cushioning and a bold new colour affectionately dubbed "Infrared", its revolutionised design helped the first 90 take on a life of its own. No longer just a running shoe, it solidified Air Max as a streetwear cornerstone.

name: Nike Air Max Tuned 1 Drift
description:
Relax in Style

Let your bold and edgy energy make waves with the Nike Air Max Tuned 1 Drift. Inspired by beach life, these cool sneakers celebrate efficiency, comfort, and a cool look! Sporting wavy design lines, the synthetic leather and mesh upper is packed with supreme comfort and a cool look. Offering signature cushioning, the Max Air unit ensures proper responsiveness with every stride. Fitted with a grippy rubber outsole, the Nike Air Max Plus has everything you need to flaunt your moves with confidence.

Nike Air Max Tuned 1 Drift Features:

  • Mesh upper
  • Wavy lines across the upper
  • Max Air unit
  • Plastic arch on the midsole
  • Rubber outsole

name: Nike Air Max Dn
description:
Feel the Shift

The Nike Air Max Dn Essential sneakers are designed with the future in mind. The Dynamic Air unit has tubes with two pressure levels that adjust as you walk. These sneakers are firm in the heel and soft in the middle, so each step feels smooth and responsive. The mesh on top is light and lets your feet breathe, and the cool texture makes the sneakers look good. From the foam midsole to the rubber outsole, every detail is designed to give you the ultimate in comfort and energy. Step into the Nike Air Max Dn Essential sneakers and take the first step toward a new level of comfort.

Nike Air Max Dn Essential Features:

  • Multilayered mesh upper
  • Haptic print on upper
  • Foam cushioning
  • Foam midsole
  • Rubber outsole
  • Dynamic Air unit system
  • Dual-pressure tubes
  • At least 20% recycled content by weight

name: Nike Air Max Tuned 3
description:
Honoring Heritage

Bring the best of the past to your new-age rotation with the Nike Air Max Plus 3. Assembling OG AM features, these sneakers honor heritage while nodding to their predecessors. A mix of synthetic leather and mesh plays on the upper to deliver supportive ease and breathable comfort throughout the day. Located at the heel and forefoot, the Max Air units boost tried-and-true cushioning in your strides. The rubber outsole is sturdy and grippy as you make the move into the future.

Nike Air Max Plus 3 Features:

  • Synthetic leather and mesh on the upper
  • Polished plastic accents on the toe
  • Max Air units in the heel and forefoot
  • Rubber outsole

name: Nike Air Max 1
description: Meet the leader of the pack. Walking on clouds above the noise, the Air Max 1 blends timeless design with cushioned comfort. Sporting a Max Air unit and mixed materials, this icon hit the scene in '87 and continues to be the soul of the franchise today. Benefits: The upper mixes synthetic leather, suede and mesh for a layered look built to last. Foam midsole with a Max Air unit in the heel provides lightweight cushioning. Rubber Waffle outsole adds durable traction and heritage style. The padded, low-cut collar feels soft and comfortable. Air Max 1: Sure, Air Max 1 started as a running shoe, but you can't keep innovation contained. Adopted by hip-hop culture, this runner with a controversial exposed Air unit could be found anywhere from the heart of Brooklyn to the streets of London. Its cutting-edge design and striking colourways, to this day, are celebrated year after year.

Remarkably Iconic

  • Foam in midsole
  • Rubber Waffle outsole

name: Nike Tuned 3
description:
Stylish Homage to Legends

Rep some running legacy with every step you take while sporting the Nike Air Max Plus 3. Taking the best from Nike’s iconic sneakers in the past, these AM shoes nod to retro futurism. The upper blends synthetic leather and mesh to deliver flexible ease and proper breathability in one go. Located at the heel and forefoot, the signature Max Air unit keeps your strides cushioned and full of energy. Enabling great traction and sure-footed grip, the rubber outsole gets you ready to step into the glorious future.

Nike Air Max Plus 3 Features:

  • Synthetic leather and mesh upper
  • Polished plastic accents on the toe
  • Max Air units in the heel and forefoot
  • Foam midsole
  • Rubber outsole

name: Nike Air Max Tuned 1
description: Let your attitude have the edge with flame-like caging that adds heat to the streets while airy mesh keeps you cool. The Nike Air Max Plus gives you a tuned Nike Air experience that offers premium stability and unbelievable cushioning. Benefits: Bringing stress-free beach life to the city, the supportive midfoot arch draws inspiration from a whale's tail. Design lines of the iconic plastic cage nod to palm trees and ocean waves. Originally designed for performance running, Nike Air units provide lightweight cushioning that lasts. Synthetic upper with lightweight mesh adds breathability and durability. Rubber outsole gives you durable traction. Nike Air Max Origins: Revolutionary Air technology first made its way into Nike footwear in 1978. The Air Max 1 debuted with visible Air technology in its heel, allowing fans more than just the feel of Air cushioning—suddenly they could see it. Since then, next-generation Air Max shoes have become a hit with athletes and collectors by offering striking colour combinations and reliable, lightweight cushioning.

name: Nike Tuned
description:
Layer Up Boldly

The Nike Sportswear Woven Track Jacket is the ultimate combo of style and function. Featuring a relaxed fit and full-length zipper, it is meant for easy layering on any day. The crinkled taffeta brings a nostalgic vibe, while the ripstop panels at the elbows add durability. Soft and breathable comfort from the inner lining makes it a cozy companion for every activity. Quick-access pockets are perfect for holding essentials or warming up cold hands. Plus, elastic cuffs and hem finish off the sleek design, ensuring this jacket stays put. Walk the streets in style with the Nike Sportswear Woven Track Jacket.

  • Body: 100% nylon
  • Panel/linings: 100% polyester
  • Loose fit
  • Full-length zipper
  • Crinkled taffeta fabric
  • Ripstop panels on elbows
  • Inner lining
  • Full-zip design
  • Pockets
  • Elastic cuffs

  • Machine wash
  • Imported

name: Nike Zoom Vomero Roam
description: Designed for city conditions, this winterized version of the Vomero is made for wet weather. Durable materials and a rubber mudguard work together to help safeguard your shoes from dirt and puddles. Plus, a chunky midsole gives you a visible boost of comfort and style wherever you wander. Benefits: The layers of textile on the upper create a durable, comfortable fit. The lace toggle is easy to adjust and features a hook to keep it in place. The water-repellent finish and rubber mudguard help block the elements so your feet stay dry. The Nike Air Zoom units provide all-day cushioning. The HART (High Abrasion Rubber Tech) outsole uses less rubber compound than our other XDR rubber technologies—without sacrificing durability and abrasion resistance. Less material helps make the outsole lighter and more flexible. Product details: Pull tabs. Reflective design details. Foam midsole. Rubber outsole. Not intended for use as personal protective equipment (PPE)

name: Nike Zoom Lebron Nxxt Gen
description:
For The Future

Feel assured, poised, and ready to take on challenges in the Nike Zoom LeBron Nxxt Gen. The breathable open-hole mesh upper provides freshness and durability, while the foam in the midsole feels soft and plush as you keep low to the ground. The Zoom Air unit in the heel adds extra responsiveness and support so you never let go of the goal in sight. The map of Akron where James LeBron’s roots originate stay with you in form of a multidirectional traction, so you are reminded of your own roots. Do it for yourself and do it right with the Nike Zoom LeBron Nxxt Gen.

Nike Zoom LeBron Nxxt Gen Features:

  • Open-hole mesh upper
  • Lace closure
  • Zoom Air unit
  • Alternate colors on left shoe and right shoe
  • Graphic sublimation on insole
  • Foam midsole
  • Multidirectional traction pattern

name: Nike Zoom Vomero Roam
description: Designed for city conditions, this winterized version of the Vomero is made for wet weather. Durable materials and a rubber mudguard work together to help safeguard your shoes from dirt and puddles. Plus, a chunky midsole gives you a visible boost of comfort and style wherever you wander. Benefits: Layers of textile and suede on the upper create a durable, comfortable fit. The lace toggle is easy to adjust and features a hook to keep it in place. The water-repellent finish and rubber mudguard help block the elements so your feet stay dry. The Nike Air Zoom units provide all-day cushioning. The HART (High-Abrasion Rubber Tech) outsole uses less rubber compound than our other XDR rubber technologies—without sacrificing durability and abrasion resistance. Less material helps make the outsole lighter and more flexible. Product details: Pull tabs. Foam midsole. Reflective design details. Not intended for use as personal protective equipment (PPE)

name: Nike Club
description: Easy to style and comfortable to wear, our Nike Club knit joggers are ready to become a versatile piece of your casual wardrobe. The relaxed fit is designed to give you a bit of room around the seat and thighs. The slight taper and ribbed ankle cuffs keep it clean around your sneakers. Pull them on with a tee or your favourite hoodie for casual, everyday wear. Benefits: The soft knit fabric feels smooth and lightweight for all-day comfort. The stretchy elastic waist with external drawcord lets you find the right fit. Ribbed ankle cuffs give you a clean look that highlights your kicks. Product details: Hand pockets. Embroidered Nike Futura logo on the left thigh. Body: 100% cotton. Rib: 98% cotton/2% elastane. Machine wash. Imported

name: Nike Air Force 1 Low
description:
Nature-inspired Comfort

Bring out your radiance in the fresh and bold style of the Nike Air Force 1 '07 LV8. Designed originally for hardwood, these sneakers featuring recycled content combine the best of sporty functionality with a touch of eco-friendliness. Adored with nature-inspired features, the classic ‘80s construction comes dressed in breathable canvas with stitched overlays to deliver long-lasting comfort and an edgy look. Ensuring incredible cushioning, the Air technology enables smooth and bouncy rides as you head out to rule the streets.

Nike Air Force 1 '07 LV8 Features:

  • Canvas upper with stitched overlays
  • Leather accents
  • Padded collar
  • Foam midsole
  • Nike Air technology
  • Rubber outsole
  • At least 20% recycled content by weight

name: Nike Sportswear Tech Fleece Slim Fit Joggers
Nike Air Max Tuned 1
description: Let your attitude have the edge with flame-like caging that adds heat to the streets while airy mesh keeps you cool. The Nike Air Max Plus gives you a tuned Nike Air experience that offers premium stability and unbelievable cushioning. Benefits: Bringing stress-free beach life to the city, the supportive midfoot arch draws inspiration from a whale's tail. Design lines of the iconic plastic cage nod to palm trees and ocean waves. Originally designed for performance running, Nike Air units provide lightweight cushioning that lasts. Synthetic upper with lightweight mesh adds breathability and durability. Rubber outsole gives you durable traction. Nike Air Max Origins: Revolutionary Air technology first made its way into Nike footwear in 1978. The Air Max 1 debuted with visible Air technology in its heel, allowing fans more than just the feel of Air cushioning—suddenly they could see it. Since then, next-generation Air Max shoes have become a hit with athletes and collectors by offering striking colour combinations and reliable, lightweight cushioning.

name: Nike Air Max 90
description: The Air Max 90 stays true to its running roots with the iconic Waffle sole. Stitched overlays and textured accents create the '90s look you love. Finished with easy-to-style colours, its visible Max Air cushioning adds comfort to your journey. Benefits: The textile upper with leather and synthetic overlays creates a layered look that lasts. Originally designed for performance running, visible Max Air cushioning puts the history of comfort beneath your feet. Rubber Waffle outsole delivers durable traction and heritage style. Product details: Padded collar. Foam midsole Air Max 90: The '90s were a turning point in culture—art, music, fashion and sneakers. The Air Max was at the forefront of the movement. With even more exposed Air cushioning and a bold new colour affectionately dubbed "Infrared", its revolutionised design helped the first 90 take on a life of its own. No longer just a running shoe, it solidified Air Max as a streetwear cornerstone.

name: Nike Air Max Dn
description:
Feel the Shift

The Nike Air Max Dn Essential sneakers are designed with the future in mind. The Dynamic Air unit has tubes with two pressure levels that adjust as you walk. These sneakers are firm in the heel and soft in the middle, so each step feels smooth and responsive. The mesh on top is light and lets your feet breathe, and the cool texture makes the sneakers look good. From the foam midsole to the rubber outsole, every detail is designed to give you the ultimate in comfort and energy. Step into the Nike Air Max Dn Essential sneakers and take the first step toward a new level of comfort.

Nike Air Max Dn Essential Features:

  • Multilayered mesh upper
  • Haptic print on upper
  • Foam cushioning
  • Foam midsole
  • Rubber outsole
  • Dynamic Air unit system
  • Dual-pressure tubes
  • At least 20% recycled content by weight

name: Nike Air Max 1
description: Meet the leader of the pack. Walking on clouds above the noise, the Air Max 1 blends timeless design with cushioned comfort. Sporting a Max Air unit and mixed materials, this icon hit the scene in '87 and continues to be the soul of the franchise today. Benefits: The upper mixes synthetic leather, suede and mesh for a layered look built to last. Foam midsole with a Max Air unit in the heel provides lightweight cushioning. Rubber Waffle outsole adds durable traction and heritage style. The padded, low-cut collar feels soft and comfortable. Air Max 1: Sure, Air Max 1 started as a running shoe, but you can't keep innovation contained. Adopted by hip-hop culture, this runner with a controversial exposed Air unit could be found anywhere from the heart of Brooklyn to the streets of London. Its cutting-edge design and striking colourways, to this day, are celebrated year after year.

Nike Air Max Tuned 1
description: Let your attitude have the edge with flame-like caging that adds heat to the streets while airy mesh keeps you cool. The Nike Air Max Plus gives you a tuned Nike Air experience that offers premium stability and unbelievable cushioning. Benefits: Bringing stress-free beach life to the city, the supportive midfoot arch draws inspiration from a whale's tail. Design lines of the iconic plastic cage nod to palm trees and ocean waves. Originally designed for performance running, Nike Air units provide lightweight cushioning that lasts. Synthetic upper with lightweight mesh adds breathability and durability. Rubber outsole gives you durable traction. Nike Air Max Origins: Revolutionary Air technology first made its way into Nike footwear in 1978. The Air Max 1 debuted with visible Air technology in its heel, allowing fans more than just the feel of Air cushioning—suddenly they could see it. Since then, next-generation Air Max shoes have become a hit with athletes and collectors by offering striking colour combinations and reliable, lightweight cushioning.

description:
Score High with Low

Ensure victory as you lace up the Nike Air Force 1 '07. Crossing hardwood comfort with off-court flair, these classic AF sneakers are pure retro vibes transmitted to the new era. Featuring subtle varsity-inspired details, the premium, durable leather upper seamlessly blends sporty comfort with street-ready style. The hidden Nike Air units deliver visible responsiveness, while the cushioned foam midsole fills your strides with all the energy you need to rule the court.

Nike Air Force 1 '07 Features:

  • Leather upper
  • Perforations on the toe
  • Low-cut, padded collar
  • Cupsole design
  • Nike Air cushioning
  • Foam midsole
  • Rubber outsole with hoops pivot circles
